Population = INTEG ( Births - Deaths, 1000 )
	~ Person
	~ A simple population stock
	|
Births = Population * Birth Fraction
	~ Person/Month
	~
	|
Deaths = Population / Average Lifetime
	~ Person/Month
	~
	|
Birth Fraction = 0.02
	~ 1/Month
	~
	|
Average Lifetime = 75
	~ Month
	~
	|
INITIAL TIME = 0
	~ Month
	~
	|
FINAL TIME = 120
	~ Month
	~
	|
TIME STEP = 0.25
	~ Month
	~
	|
SAVEPER = TIME STEP
	~ Month
	~
	|
